UNIX BUILD
==========

Requirements
------------

You'll need the Gtk development headers.

Configure
---------

Default configure

$ ./configure

or specify one or more of the configure options:

$ ./configure --prefix=... --with-tcl=... --with-tk=... --with-gtk-inc=... --with-gtk-lib=...

Default value for gtk-inc: /usr/include/gtk
Default value for gtk-lib: /usr/lib

Build
-----

$ make

Install
-------

$ make install
